Hi Emil Skogsund,
This is the last day of our Launch Week and the best comes for last: 🧪 Prompt Experiments in Langfuse.
 
With Prompt Experiments in Langfuse, you can test and evaluate different prompt versions and models on thousands of dataset items
simultaneously. You can perform live llm-as-a-judge evaluations and compare the results side-by-side – all within the UI for
faster iterations on your app, without causing regressions :)
 
Watch the Launch Video on Product Hunt [https://langfuse.com/ph] to learn more!
 
We'd greatly appreciate your support if you provide feedback or an upvote (if you like it) on Product Hunt! This helps us spread
the word and grow the Langfuse community.
 

